x^n-1=(x-1)(x^{n-1}+x^{n-2}+\cdots +x+1).
\begin{align}(x-1)(x^{n-1}+x^{n-2}+\cdots +x+1)=x(x^{n-1}+x^{n-2}+\cdots +x+1)\\-(x^{n-1}+x^{n-2}+\cdots +x&+1)\end{align}.
